## Maintenance and Best Practices

### Security Recommendations
- Rotate AWS credentials regularly
- Use IAM roles instead of access keys where possible
- Enable MFA for AWS root account
- Store sensitive data in AWS Secrets Manager
- Use RBAC in Kubernetes
- Scan Docker images for vulnerabilities (Trivy)

### Monitoring
- Configure CloudWatch alarms for EC2 metrics
- Set up Kubernetes monitoring with Prometheus/Grafana
- Enable ArgoCD notifications
- Monitor Jenkins build metrics

### Backup Strategy
- Backup Terraform state file
- Export Jenkins configuration
- Backup Kubernetes manifests
- Document manual configuration changes

### Scaling Considerations
- Increase replica count in deployment.yaml
- Use Horizontal Pod Autoscaler (HPA)
- Configure cluster autoscaling for EKS
- Optimize Docker image size

